lApp`, not URL path segments. Entry navigation comes from the role-specific sidebar, the top bar, and cross-link handlers in [`src/App.tsx`](../../src/App.tsx).\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:40:| `faculty-profile` | `FacultyProfilePage` | Cross-cutting route | Sidebar faculty-profile button; `handleOpenStudentProfile` may route here for mentor/self profile views. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:41:| `student-history` | `StudentHistoryPage` | Cross-cutting route | Student cards, mentee cards, queue items, history cross-links. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:42:| `student-shell` | `StudentShellPage` | Cross-cutting route | Student history cross-link, student drawer, proof controls. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:43:| `risk-explorer` | `RiskExplorerPage` | Cross-cutting route | Student history cross-link, student drawer, proof controls. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:45:Role gating is enforced by [`src/academic-workspace-route-helpers.ts`](../../src/academic-workspace-route-helpers.ts):\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:58:| `#/admin/overview` | `SystemAdminLiveApp` overview workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Default admin landing route. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:59:| `#/admin/proof-dashboard` | Proof dashboard workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Proof-scoped admin surface. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:60:| `#/admin/students` | Student registry workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Registry list route. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:61:| `#/admin/students/:studentId` | Student detail workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Direct entity drilldown. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:62:| `#/admin/faculty-members` | Faculty registry workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Registry list route. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:63:| `#/admin/faculty-members/:facultyMemberId` | Faculty detail workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Direct entity drilldown. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:64:| `#/admin/requests` | Governed requests workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` and some `HOD`-backed flows | List route. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:65:| `#/admin/requests/:requestId` | Request detail workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` and some `HOD`-backed flows | Direct entity drilldown. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:66:| `#/admin/history` | Hidden-records / recycle-bin workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Restore and archive history. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:67:| `#/admin/faculties` | University hierarchy workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Sectioned registry workspace. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:68:| `#/admin/faculties/:academicFacultyId` | Faculty-level hierarchy workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Base faculty scope. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:69:| `#/admin/faculties/:academicFacultyId/departments/:departmentId` | Department-level hierarchy workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Department drilldown. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:70:| `#/admin/faculties/:academicFacultyId/departments/:departmentId/branches/:branchId` | Branch-level hierarchy workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Branch drilldown. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:71:| `#/admin/faculties/:academicFacultyId/departments/:departmentId/branches/:branchId/batches/:batchId` | Batch-level hierarchy workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Batch drilldown; canonical proof route extends here. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:73:The canonical proof route helper in [`src/proof-pilot.ts`](../../src/proof-pilot.ts) maps to:\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:75:- `#/admin/faculties/academic_faculty_engineering_and_technology/departments/dept_cse/branches/branch_mnc_btech/batches/batch_branch_mnc_btech_2023`\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:94:### Admin helper-generated routes\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:96:- `routeToHash()` and `parseAdminRoute()` in [`src/system-admin-live-app.tsx`](../../src/system-admin-live-app.tsx) are the canonical serializer/parser pair.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route